      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over perfection. The engine and transmission are functional and have been regularly serviced, but the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done but definitely shows the character of its miles.",
