    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in mint condition, meticulously maintained to meet the most exacting standards of discerning collectors and enthusiasts alike. Every facet of this automobile, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, showroom-quality interior, reflects a history of uncompromising care. Mechanically superior and aesthetically peerless, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of significant distinction.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
